\date{2026-03-01}
\import{table-macros}
\title{Welcome, [[kaiphan]] and [[edwinpark]]!}
\author{liamoc}
\p{I have taken on another PhD student, [[kaiphan]], who (at least to start) will conduct some investigations into incorrectness logic, along with me, [[xinloi]], and [[hoefner]].  Welcome, Kai!}
\p{[[edwinpark]], a new honours student, has also arrived from [[unimelb]] to do an honours project with me here at the ANU. We are looking at program calculational techniques such as [[ccm]]'s refinement calculus, and exploring proof-assistant-integrated program calculation techniques.}